I have a User Macro that contains an iframe.
{quote}
(No macro body)
Template:
{code}
## @noparams
<iframe src="https://example.com"></iframe>
{code}
{quote}

When i insert this macro into a page all content that comes after it doesn't get displayed. Somehow the macro breaks the page.
I found a workaround though. If i add an html macro with {{</iframe>}} after the user macro, it works fine.
Also when i add an iframe directly (with the html macro) everything gets displayed properly.

